headline: GTA Online
subtitle: New Rides
content:
Two brand new muscle cars have been added for sale on Benny’s new website, along with a selection of Benny’s other favorite project cars that can all be uniquely modded at his garage.

Add quad pump hydraulics to the Willard Faction for some serious lift, or load your crew into the Declasse Moonbeam and fire weapons out of the passenger sliding doors.
